rules_text:
First mate – Your starting deck contains “[i]Seaskipper[/i]” and at least eight cards with an alternate cost. [i](If this card outside the game is your chosen first mate, you may swap it with a card in your opening hand.)[/i]
At the beginning of your end step, if you don’t control a 0/1 green Kelp creature token with “{T}: Add {G},” create one.
